ed="T" n="0842a12"/><persName key="A012760">釋神鑒</persName>，姓<name>韓</name>氏，<placeName key="PL000000018846">潯陽</placeName>人也。穉歲淳靜，而不<lb
ed="T" n="0842a13"/>雜群童。父為<placeName key="PL000000026549">齊安</placeName>掾，且歸心<name>釋</name>氏，甞於廨<lb
ed="T" n="0842a14"/>署陳像設，命僧徒讚唄揚音，法樂俱作。<persName key="A012760">鑒</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0842a15"/>則喜色盈顏，隨僧不捨，求願出家。父母無<lb
ed="T" n="0842a16"/>計阻之，潛投<placeName key="PL000000018801">東林寺</placeName><persName key="A012763">貞素<roleName>律師</roleName></persName>下修學。後<lb
ed="T" n="0842a17"/>講通大涅槃經義，乃南格<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1662"/><placeName key="PL000000018603">豫章</placeName>，參<persName key="A003623">大寂<roleName>禪<lb
ed="T" n="0842a18"/>師</roleName></persName>。續於<placeName key="PL000000026303">懷安</placeName>西北山居焉。是山先是猛獸旁<lb
ed="T" n="0842a19"/>午<ptr type="glossary" target="#g89"/>，率多作害。從<persName key="A012760">鑒</persName>居之，虎災弭息，遠近稱<lb
ed="T" n="0842a20"/>之。忽有戴平<anchor xml:id="beg0842sgsz3"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic><g ref="#Z1277"/></sic><corr>幘</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0842sgsz3"/>男子，望法座致<anchor xml:id="beg0842sgsz5"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0842sgsz5"/>勤重<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g250"/>，<lb
ed="T" n="0842a21"/>倏爾無蹤。七日後有冠裳宛異者，於方丈<lb
ed="T" n="0842a22"/>前升空宣言曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A012760">此大師</ref>者，真法寶也。開人<lb
ed="T" n="0842a23"/>天眼目，故來報之。」其徒聞見，知<persName key="A012760">鑒</persName>道高。<date from-iso="+0844-01-28" key="j20293522029735" to-iso="+0845-02-14"><name>會<lb
ed="T" n="0842a24"/>昌</name>四年</date>入滅，<date key="j20296022029602" when-iso="+0844-10-04">八月十五日</date>藏之于塔。凡得道<lb
ed="T" n="0842a25"/>之人，地神報空神，展轉至于<name>有頂</name><ptr type="glossary" target="#g1203"/>，於斯見<lb
ed="T" n="0842a26"/>矣。</p>
